          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "That’s not a run in just the dozens, but we think those cars are going to sell out quickly. Another 50 ZL1 Collector’s Edition cars are going to markets outside the US, like Canada and Japan. Of course, GM isn’t confirming these claims, so for now it’s all speculation. However, it has said global production is capped at 350 units, so we think this info is likely accurate.",
